  "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-main relative\"\u003e\n \u003ch1 class\u003d\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\"\u003eNATO b\u0026aacute;o động, điều ti\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch Typhoon đ\u0026aacute;nh chặn m\u0026aacute;y bay Nga\u003c/h1\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n   \u003ca href\u003d\"/bao-cong-ly-cong-ly-p236.epi\" class\u003d\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o C\u0026ocirc;ng L\u0026yacute;\"\u003e\n    \u003cfigure class\u003d\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style\u003d\"width:52.5px;height:20px\" aria-label\u003d\"Logo nh\u0026agrave; xuất bản\"\u003e\n     \u003cpicture\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/cf80b1ef6cac85f2dcbd.png\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/cf80b1ef6cac85f2dcbd.png\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003cimg src\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/cf80b1ef6cac85f2dcbd.png\" alt\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o C\u0026ocirc;ng L\u0026yacute;\" width\u003d\"168\" height\u003d\"64\" /\u003e\n     \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n   \u003cspan\u003e\u003cbutton class\u003d\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex\u003d\"0\" type\u003d\"button\" title\u003d\"Theo d\u0026otilde;i \u0026quot;C\u0026ocirc;ng L\u0026yacute;\u0026quot;\" aria-label\u003d\"Button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-24T07:24:00.000Z\"\u003e24/10/2025\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/estonia-t41165766.epi\" class\u003d\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e55\n   \u003c!-- --\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n quan\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/nato-bao-dong-dieu-tiem-kich-typhoon-danh-chan-may-bay-nga-r53573545.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003eTối 23/10, hai m\u0026aacute;y bay qu\u0026acirc;n sự Nga bị c\u0026aacute;o buộc vi phạm kh\u0026ocirc;ng phận Litva khi bay từ khu vực Kaliningrad, khiến NATO phải lập tức triển khai lực lượng ứng ph\u0026oacute;.\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo th\u0026ocirc;ng b\u0026aacute;o từ Bộ Quốc ph\u0026ograve;ng Litva, vụ việc xảy ra v\u0026agrave;o khoảng 18h (giờ địa phương) gần thị trấn Kibartai, s\u0026aacute;t bi\u0026ecirc;n giới với \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/lien-bang-nga-tag117.epi\"\u003eNga\u003c/a\u003e. Qu\u0026acirc;n đội Litva cho biết một ti\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch Su-30 v\u0026agrave; một m\u0026aacute;y bay tiếp dầu Il-76 của Nga đ\u0026atilde; vượt qua bi\u0026ecirc;n giới trong l\u0026uacute;c thực h\u0026agrave;nh tiếp nhi\u0026ecirc;n liệu tr\u0026ecirc;n kh\u0026ocirc;ng.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:464px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"M\u0026aacute;y bay Su-30SM của Nga\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"464\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eM\u0026aacute;y bay Su-30SM của Nga\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e“C\u0026aacute;c m\u0026aacute;y bay Nga đ\u0026atilde; bay s\u0026acirc;u khoảng 700 m\u0026eacute;t v\u0026agrave;o kh\u0026ocirc;ng phận của \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/nato-tag10899.epi\"\u003eNATO\u003c/a\u003e v\u0026agrave; lưu lại khoảng 18 gi\u0026acirc;y trước khi rời khỏi khu vực”, Bộ Quốc ph\u0026ograve;ng Litva n\u0026ecirc;u r\u0026otilde;.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eNgay sau khi ph\u0026aacute;t hiện t\u0026iacute;n hiệu x\u0026acirc;m nhập, NATO điều khẩn cấp c\u0026aacute;c \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/may-bay-quan-su-tag385.epi\"\u003eti\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch\u003c/a\u003e Eurofighter Typhoon của T\u0026acirc;y Ban Nha để đ\u0026aacute;nh chặn v\u0026agrave; gi\u0026aacute;m s\u0026aacute;t khu vực vi phạm.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eC\u0026aacute;c m\u0026aacute;y bay NATO hiện tiếp tục tuần tra tr\u0026ecirc;n kh\u0026ocirc;ng phận ph\u0026iacute;a t\u0026acirc;y Litva nhằm ngăn ngừa nguy cơ t\u0026aacute;i diễn sự cố.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003ePh\u0026iacute;a qu\u0026acirc;n đội Litva cho biết đang phối hợp với cơ quan kiểm so\u0026aacute;t kh\u0026ocirc;ng lưu v\u0026agrave; lực lượng NATO để x\u0026aacute;c minh chi tiết diễn biến vụ việc, đồng thời khẳng định h\u0026agrave;nh vi tr\u0026ecirc;n “c\u0026oacute; thể mang t\u0026iacute;nh khi\u0026ecirc;u kh\u0026iacute;ch trong bối cảnh khu vực đang căng thẳng”.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTrong những th\u0026aacute;ng gần đ\u0026acirc;y, c\u0026aacute;c nước v\u0026ugrave;ng Baltic nhiều lần c\u0026aacute;o buộc Nga c\u0026oacute; h\u0026agrave;nh động x\u0026acirc;m phạm kh\u0026ocirc;ng phận. Tuy nhi\u0026ecirc;n ph\u0026iacute;a Nga đều phủ nhận c\u0026aacute;o buộc n\u0026agrave;y.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:415px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Ti\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch Eurofighter Typhoon\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"415\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eTi\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch Eurofighter Typhoon\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eHồi th\u0026aacute;ng 9, \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/estonia-tag927.epi\"\u003eEstonia\u003c/a\u003e cũng c\u0026aacute;o buộc ba ti\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch MiG-31 của Nga bay v\u0026agrave;o kh\u0026ocirc;ng phận gần đảo Vaindlo m\u0026agrave; kh\u0026ocirc;ng c\u0026oacute; kế hoạch bay, tắt hệ thống nhận dạng v\u0026agrave; kh\u0026ocirc;ng li\u0026ecirc;n lạc với kiểm so\u0026aacute;t kh\u0026ocirc;ng lưu địa phương. Nh\u0026oacute;m m\u0026aacute;y bay n\u0026agrave;y ở lại khu vực trong gần 12 ph\u0026uacute;t trước khi rời đi.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTuy nhi\u0026ecirc;n Bộ Quốc ph\u0026ograve;ng Nga phủ nhận c\u0026aacute;o buộc. Theo ph\u0026iacute;a Nga, 3 chiếc MiG-31 đ\u0026atilde; thực hiện chuyến bay thường lệ từ Karelia, ph\u0026iacute;a đ\u0026ocirc;ng Phần Lan, đến một s\u0026acirc;n bay ở v\u0026ugrave;ng Kaliningrad.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eBộ Quốc ph\u0026ograve;ng Nga khẳng định, c\u0026aacute;c m\u0026aacute;y bay nước n\u0026agrave;y đ\u0026atilde; bay qua v\u0026ugrave;ng biển trung lập tr\u0026ecirc;n biển Baltic, c\u0026aacute;ch đảo Vaindloo của Estonia hơn 3km, v\u0026agrave; \u0026quot;kh\u0026ocirc;ng x\u0026acirc;m phạm kh\u0026ocirc;ng phận Estonia\u0026quot;.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNgọc An\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"S